				<td colspan="2"><span>Oh, it's &quot;OVER haste&quot;.  Well the caps alone make it good, and worth the mile of stretching to make the car analogy stick..and while thus extended, let's take muse/riz into the scope of my worthless comment, despite them being nowhere near comparable.
<br />

<br />
15% overhaste doesn't add a straight 15% to a group's melee DPS, it adds nowhere near that.  Troub maces (let alone epics) aren't just handed out upon reaching a certain level, and can be difficult to aquire at times even on a server as old and well populated as the one I play on; even if they were given out with your backpack* I'd suggest taking a long hard look at the benefits of wielding one as opposed to a higher ratio weapon more than situationally.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
