I seem to remember (from about 2 years ago) there were reports that overhaste songs were bugged - in that if you sang them when there was no normal haste (sung or cast) the overhaste in fact slowed.  This may be what people are refering to - I never noticed it and if it was indeed true it's been long fixed.</span></td>
